  "name": "Forest Battlefield",
  "description": "A dense symmetrical forest battlefield for two active players, built around road reading, ambush woods, hill control, side objectives, and two neutral barracks. There are no rivers, bridges, or mountains. Roads deliberately route around hills instead of crossing over them.",
